Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟巢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一共在孵五个蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有四个孵化了  还剩下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想弄来吃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.42,0:01:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在关注啦  老师你就想着吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来客人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？没人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的确是在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖怪写的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  这不是确实写着的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这是只有我们才看得见的那一类东西
